title: Practice Cake
description: Maddie is a young woman trying to figure out life after high school.When she takes a job at a family-run bakery, her life gets exciting. There's a bad boy coworker to flirt with, new baked goods to invent, plus a reality TV show filming on location.Now Maddie's the star of a baking show, plus she's got two cute boys vying for her attention. Can she believe all the good things that are happening? Or is it all a plot for ratings?
author: Dalya Moon
